<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="302" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1282,1487]" pageId="9" pageNumber="302">
Two specimens, one male of 
<quantity box="[529,599,1318,1343]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" pageId="9" pageNumber="302" unit="cm" value="45.0">45 cm</quantity>
and one female of 
<quantity box="[818,902,1319,1343]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.09" pageId="9" pageNumber="302" unit="cm" value="109.0">109 cm</quantity>
TL, were caught at depth unknown, during the hauling of the bottom longline (
<bibRefCitation author="Banon" box="[511,719,1354,1379]" pageId="9" pageNumber="329" refString="Banon, R., Casas, J. M. Pineiro C. G. &amp; Covelo, M. (1997) Capturas de peces de afinidades tropicales en aguas atlanticas de Galicia (NO de la peninsula Iberica). Boletin del Instituto Espanol de Oceanografia, 13, 57 - 66." type="journal article" year="1997">
Bañón 
<emphasis box="[594,651,1354,1379]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="302">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[659,719,1355,1379]" pageId="9" pageNumber="302" value="1997.0">1997</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Habitat and Distribution: pelagic and oceanic, occurring from over the edge of continental and insular shelves into the open ocean at depths of 
<quantity box="[1058,1157,1391,1415]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.91" metricValueMax="3.81" metricValueMin="0.01" pageId="9" pageNumber="302" unit="m" value="191.0" valueMax="381.0" valueMin="1.0">1–381 m</quantity>
usually in the upper 
<number box="[1394,1436,1391,1415]" pageId="9" pageNumber="302" value="100.0">100</number>
meters. Tropical and subtropical seas, including eastern Atlantic, western Atlantic, eastern Pacific and northwestern Pacific (
<collectingCountry box="[396,461,1463,1487]" name="Japan" pageId="9" pageNumber="302">Japan</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[516,603,1462,1487]" name="Taiwan" pageId="9" pageNumber="302">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
). Vulnerability: LC (
<collectionCode box="[835,909,1463,1487]" pageId="9" pageNumber="302">IUCN</collectionCode>
), HHV (FishBase).
</paragraph>
